      <content><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><strong>Step 1</strong>. Open the <a title="Demo application" href="%(link0)" target="_blank" rel="noopener">demo application</a>.</li>
<li><strong>Step 2</strong>. See how the page looks like in the <a title="Editable web view" href="%(link1)" target="_blank" rel="noopener">editable web view</a> (requires login). The view shows one and the same content in many different display variations (image left, image right, only image, etc.).</li>
<li><strong>Step 3</strong>. From the web view, open the element settings editor.</li>
<li><strong>Step 4</strong>. Play with the different settings, click save, and see how the changes are reflected in the demo application.</li>
